title: 8.3.2.3.4.3 {(NQN, IP, Protocol), Role} Zone Member Type (Type 2h)

content.text:
This Zone member type identifies a specific fabric interface (i.e., through the IP address) and the specific
IP protocol (e.g., TCP) used by the NVMe-oF entity identified by the Zone memberâ€™s NQN over that fabric
interface. The format of this Zone member type is shown in Figure 744.
